detailedDescription.articleBody: Abdul Rashid Salim Salman Khan is an Indian film actor, producer, occasional singer and television personality who works in Hindi films.

detailedDescription.articleBody:
Rajneesh, also known as Acharya Rajneesh, Bhagwan Shri Rajneesh, and later as Osho, was an Indian godman, mystic, and founder of the Rajneesh movement.
During his lifetime, he was viewed as a controversial new religious movement leader and mystic.

detailedDescription.articleBody: Chandra Danette Wilson is an American actress and director, known for her role as Dr. Miranda Bailey in the ABC television drama Grey's Anatomy since 2005, for which she has been nominated for the Emmy for Best Supporting Actress four times.
detailedDescription.articleBodyHi: चंद्र डेनेट विल्सन एक अमेरिकी अभिनेत्री और निर्देशक हैं, जिन्हें 2005 से एबीसी टेलीविजन नाटक ग्रेज़ एनाटॉमी में डॉ मिरांडा बेली के रूप में उनकी भूमिका के लिए जाना जाता है, जिसके लिए उन्हें चार बार सर्वश्रेष्ठ सहायक अभिनेत्री के लिए एमी के लिए नामांकित किया गया है
